{
  "id": 5225615177023488,
  "name": "Web Speech API contextual biasing",
  "summary": "This feature enables websites to support contextual biasing for speech recognition by adding a recognition phrase list to the Web Speech API.\n\nDevelopers can provide a list of phrases as well as updating them to apply a bias to the speech recognition models in favor of those phrases. This helps improve accuracy and relevance for domain-specific and personalized speech recognition. ",
