  "motivation": "The Web Speech API is a web standard API that allows developers to incorporate speech recognition and synthesis into their web pages. Currently the Web Speech API uses generalized speech recognition models and cannot prioritize certain words or phrases, or adapt to user-specific or domain-specific vocabularies. Adding recognition phrase list provides the Web Speech API with an explicit mechanism to support contextual biasing.",
